						<summary>

						<p>This is slightly damaged. It seems to record a grant of land to the survivor of certain Rājēndraśōḻachcheṭṭi of Mēlai Mārā[ya*]pāḍi in Koyyakurai-nāḍu, a division of Iraṭṭapāḍikoṇḍaśōḻa-maṇḍalam, who probably lost his life in the cause of the village.</p>						

						</summary>
